The '''Raggeds Wilderness''' is a [[U.S. Wilderness Area]] located northwest of [[Crested Butte, Colorado|Crested Butte]], [[Colorado]].   The {{convert|64992|acre|km2|adj=on}} wilderness established in 1980 in the [[White River National Forest|White River]] and [[Gunnison National Forest|Gunnison]] national forests has {{convert|50|mi|km}} of trails.  

